Puppet module: cron

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages cron
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include cron              # Install and run cron with standard configurations.
include cron::disable     # Disable cron service.
include cron::disableboot # Disable cron service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include cron::absent      # Remove cron package.

DEPENDENCIES:
